{"id":191,"date":"2023-10-03T15:05:00","date_gmt":"2023-10-03T20:05:00","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/tuckermccumber.com\/?p=191"},"modified":"2023-10-08T02:10:00","modified_gmt":"2023-10-08T07:10:00","slug":"new-scenery","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/tuckermccumber.com\/2023\/10\/03\/new-scenery\/","title":{"rendered":"New Scenery"},"content":{"rendered":"<p>Aaaand we&#8217;re in Eau Claire!!! It&#8217;s been a long couple of hours doing this today. The biggest thing was finding a Transfer unit that would do this for free<\/p>\n<p>We were able to find one and a crew. We departed Duluth at approximately 1:30 and made it safely to Eau Claire at around 2:45. I&#8217;m grateful for having friends in low places. I&#8217;m settled in to Eau Claire and as you know me I have quickly adapted to the climate and the food selections. Thank you again to everyone that has made this possible.<\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_194\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-194\" style=\"width: 640px\" class=\"wp-caption alignleft\"><a href=\"https:\/\/tuckermccumber.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/10\/PXL_20231002_190843688-scaled.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-large wp-image-194\" src=\"https:\/\/tuckermccumber.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/10\/PXL_20231002_190843688-771x1024.jpg\" alt=\"Views\" width=\"640\" height=\"850\" srcset=\"https:\/\/tuckermccumber.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/10\/PXL_20231002_190843688-771x1024.jpg 771w, https:\/\/tuckermccumber.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/10\/PXL_20231002_190843688-226x300.jpg 226w, https:\/\/tuckermccumber.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/10\/PXL_20231002_190843688-768x1020.jpg 768w, https:\/\/tuckermccumber.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/10\/PXL_20231002_190843688-1157x1536.jpg 1157w, https:\/\/tuckermccumber.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/10\/PXL_20231002_190843688-1542x2048.jpg 1542w, https:\/\/tuckermccumber.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/10\/PXL_20231002_190843688-1024x1360.jp